1 REM "This program calculates the BMI, meant to test a bit complex calculations"
2 IMPRIME "Ce programme te donne ton IMC"
3 NL
4 IMPRIME "Donne ton poids [KG]: "
5 ENTREE P
6 IMPRIME "Donne ta taille [en cm]: "
7 ENTREE T
8 B = ((10 * P * 100 * 100) / (T * T))
9 IMPRIME "Ton IMC (BMI) est ", B / 10, ".", (B - (B/10)*10)
10 NL
11 I = 185
12 N = I + 64
13 E = N + (((-1) * (-10)) + 40)
14 O = E + 100




15 SI B < I ALORS VAVERS I

16 SI B < N ALORS VAVERS N

17 SI B < E ALORS VAVERS E

18 SI B < O ALORS VAVERS O

19 VAVERS 1000

